data.description:
Welcome to this former model home, designed with sophistication and practicality in mind. Every detail has been carefully chosen to create a warm and inviting atmosphere. Step inside to find upgraded shiplap walls and wide plank floors, leading you to an open floor plan with an upgraded kitchen and adjoining living area. The spacious living room features a sleek modern fireplace, while the kitchen offers quartz counters and stainless appliances. Relax on the large screened back porch, perfect for year-round enjoyment. The primary bedroom on the main floor includes an upgraded tiled shower. Upstairs, discover four additional bedrooms, each nicely separated. One upper bedroom can serve as a second family room or flex space. Tasteful wallpaper selections enhance the ambiance. 
Experience seamless connectivity with Fiber Highspeed Internet. Modern amenities, catering to comfort and functionality for discerning homebuyers. Grass has been enhanced in photos.
